lead_paragraph: Newcastle United's Aleksandar Mitrovic scored twice against Preston North End for the second time in five days as the Championship leaders won 2-1 at Deepdale on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Newcastle's Mitrovic Inflicts More Pain on Preston
